    public interface WithJsonDiscriminator
extends Serializable
    Represent an object which can be serialize to JSON. Implementing this interface force serialization of class discriminator in "@class" property.

    Default @class value is the concrete class simple name but it can be overriden with JsonClassName annotation

    Author:
    maxence
